53:16.042 --> 53:29.000
And every day I am more 
confident in you. 


53:30.523 --> 53:34.093
This month we have seen 
how trusting in Jehovah 


53:34.093 --> 53:38.498
and his guidance 
can assist us in a variety of ways: 


53:38.498 --> 53:41.166
addressing issues with a close friend, 


53:41.167 --> 53:43.737
our choices in entertainment, 


53:43.737 --> 53:48.074
and even coping with a world 
filled with social injustice. 


53:48.073 --> 53:52.245
Certainly, Jehovah 
is someone in whom we can trust! 


53:52.245 --> 53:57.083
But we have one last treat 
for you before we end our program. 


53:57.083 --> 54:01.688
We’ll briefly travel to Cádiz, Spain. 


54:01.688 --> 54:06.058
Cádiz is considered to be one 
of the oldest cities in Western Europe 


54:06.058 --> 54:08.361
and was founded by the Phoenicians. 


54:08.362 --> 54:13.734
It is situated on a narrow slice 
of land surrounded by the sea. 


54:13.733 --> 54:16.970
Cádiz has a wealth of vistas 


54:16.970 --> 54:20.240
and well-preserved historical landmarks. 


54:20.240 --> 54:24.377
On the outskirts 
lies Puerto de Santa María, 


54:24.377 --> 54:27.447
where an English-speaking 
congregation meets. 


54:27.447 --> 54:30.217
This congregation is made up mainly 


54:30.217 --> 54:33.554
of brothers and sisters 
serving as need-greaters. 


54:33.553 --> 54:37.903
They have come from other parts 
of Spain as well as distant lands, 


54:37.903 --> 54:42.928
such as Australia, Britain, 
Canada, and the United States. 


54:42.928 --> 54:46.035
Cádiz has a high rate of unemployment, 


54:46.035 --> 54:48.068
so finding work is not easy. 


54:48.068 --> 54:52.540
One couple travels nearly 300 miles 


54:52.540 --> 54:54.473
(or 483 km) 


54:54.473 --> 54:57.210
every Thursday to their territory, 


54:57.210 --> 55:01.748
and on Monday morning they make 
the trip back to where they live and work. 


55:01.748 --> 55:04.416
In spite of these financial challenges, 


55:04.417 --> 55:07.520
many are still serving 
as construction volunteers, 


55:07.520 --> 55:11.573
remote Bethel workers, and pioneers. 


55:11.573 --> 55:14.910
Our brothers and sisters 
in Puerto de Santa María 


55:14.910 --> 55:18.882
are thrilled to send their love 
and greetings to you all. 


55:18.882 --> 55:21.650
This is JW Broadcasting 


55:21.650 --> 55:31.795
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses. 

